snippet.title: SPEED DREAMS - 1967 Grand Prix at Brondehach
snippet.description:
We travelled back in time to the British Brondehach circuit in the south of England, this time with the Guthrie Eagle of the "1967 Grand Prix" category.  Handling these beasts with a 3L V12 engine and no downforce is a real challenge that requires all 5 senses, as you can see in the video.

You can find this game and more info about this Open Source project on:
https://www.speed-dreams.net 

"Surf Shimmy" Kevin MacLeod (incompetech.com)
